Key Match Events: Rohit Sharma scored 87 runs off 101 balls.
Jasprit Bumrah took 3 wickets for 32 runs.
Mohammed Shami took 4 wickets for 22 runs.
Pre-Game Insights: England elected to field first after winning the toss.
Post-Match Reflections: Rohit Sharma was named Player of the Match for his 87 runs.
India earned 2 points from the match.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Bharat Ratna Shri Atal Bihari Vajpayee Ekana Cricket Stadium, Lucknow.
The match was part of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023.
